        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer258901488" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11467111540530235761">Okay, so I&apos;m now of fan of Lane Diamond&apos;s. I read 3 of his short stories before I read this book, so I had high expectations. I wasn&apos;t disappointed.<br/><br/>Based on some of his stories, Diamond likes to get inside the head of his characters. He&apos;s a mind meddler, and he&apos;s good at it.<br/><br/>His characters just snap, and feel real. This story had some familiar elements, but his handling of the characters makes it a great read. I don&apos;t want to spoil anything, but based on the ending, I&apos;m really looking forward to </span>
  <span id="freeText11467111540530235761" style="display:none">Okay, so I'm now of fan of Lane Diamond's. I read 3 of his short stories before I read this book, so I had high expectations. I wasn't disappointed.<br /><br />Based on some of his stories, Diamond likes to get inside the head of his characters. He's a mind meddler, and he's good at it.<br /><br />His characters just snap, and feel real. This story had some familiar elements, but his handling of the characters makes it a great read. I don't want to spoil anything, but based on the ending, I'm really looking forward to his next book.</span>
